body_html:
I solved the problem through the stackoverflow link below. I fixed the problem by adding the option --linkopt = '- llog'.

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/48850364/failed-to-load-android-log-print-in-libtensorflowlite-jni-so/48850600#48850600?newreg=7a617742737e420fb1846cc2406323a2

bazel build -c opt
--config = android_arm
--cxxopt = '- std = c ++ 11'
--linkopt = '- llog'
tensorflow / contrib / lite / tools / benchmark: benchmark_model

body:
I solved the problem through the stackoverflow link below. I fixed the problem by adding the option --linkopt = '- llog'.

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/48850364/failed-to-load-android-log-print-in-libtensorflowlite-jni-so/48850600#48850600?newreg=7a617742737e420fb1846cc2406323a2

bazel build -c opt \
--config = android_arm \
--cxxopt = '- std = c ++ 11' \
--linkopt = '- llog' \
tensorflow / contrib / lite / tools / benchmark: benchmark_model
